'''Janel Chase''' is the girlfriend of Corey Ramsey.

==History==
Janel came to the hospital when her boyfriend, Corey, was in a car accident. She told the doctors that despite what [[Patricia Ramsey|his wife]] had said, Corey would rather live with the mental deficits than die.

She stayed at the hospital and went into his room to hold his hand while Patricia was out of the room. When Patricia learned that Janel was pregnant, she decided that it wasn't solely her decision to make and they agreed to let Corey have the surgery.

After his surgery, they said they had to remove more of his brain than they expected and it would be a long recovery. While Janel went to see him in recovery, Patricia left the hospital.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
She is dating Corey Ramsey. They met four years prior to his accident. The night of his accident, she told him she was pregnant.
